Annotation Type HelperCodes


  • @Retention(value=SOURCE)
public @interface HelperCodes
    Created by Keval on 08/04/18. Error codes to detect the error from the fingerprint authentication. This error codes are for the errors which are recoverable. Fingerprint authentication won't terminate once the any of these error code occurs.
